"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-paris-paralympics-2024-everything-you-need-to-know\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9353894899400291, \"rank\": 0.05508193648884243, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbParis Paralympics 2024: Everything you need to know  The Paris Paralympics 2024, runs from 28 August to 8 September, it promises to be a spectacular event with over 4,000 athletes.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9353894899400291, \"rank\": 0.05508193648884243, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 261, \"end\": 266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.776260983737146e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stage is set for the Paris Paralympics 2024.\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.776260983737146e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From 28 August to 8 September, the City of Lights will host over 4,000 athletes from more than 150 nations.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These nations will compete across 22 sports.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This event marks the first time France has hosted the Summer Paralympics.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7297658465771051, \"rank\": 0.3702694483918308, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of the Olympic venues, such as Roland Garros and the Stade de France are being repurposed for the games.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 699, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 0.7854184769252045, \"rank\": 0.2732066145357142, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The anticipation is palpable, and here's everything you need to know to get ready.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 856, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mark your calendars.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony kicks off on 28 August, with the first day of competition following on 29 August, according toThe Telegraph.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Events will run daily, with start times similar to those of the Olympics, ensuring a full day of thrilling action.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The closing ceremony will take place on 8 September, bringing the curtain down on what promises to be a spectacular event.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are planning to witness the action in person, there is still time to grab tickets.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prices are reasonable, with day-long Discovery Passes available for \\u20ac24(R500),allowing access to several sessions throughout the day.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For those seeking a more luxurious experience, pricier options are available in the hospitality sections.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tickets can be bought directly from the official Paralympics website.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Forget stadium ceremonies.\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Paralympics will dazzle viewers with its unique opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999962424226, \"rank\": 3.757470397860056e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The backdrop of some of Paris' most iconic landmarks will set the scene.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1786, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.776260983737146e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eiffel Tower, Place de la Concorde, and the Trocad\\u00e9ro will serve as the stage for a spectacle like no other.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2224779466679441e-17, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}, {\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"score\": 0.9730907954876998, \"rank\": 0.023351147168026228, \"text\": \"Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thomas Jolly, the artistic director for the ceremonies, shared his excitement.\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1950, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"score\": 0.9985713450566273, \"rank\": 0.001140923651918765, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While the Paris Paralympics 2024 Opening Ceremony will be the first of its kind, its monumental and popular concept is, for me, first and foremost a magnificent source of inspiration.\\\"\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2041, \"end\": 2046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.776260983737146e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2064, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9994117068858733, \"rank\": 0.0005399702264864397, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He promises a \\\"spectacle that will showcase the Paralympic athletes and the values that they embody\\\", according to theInternational Paralympic Committee.\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Expect something truly special as Paris transforms into a live performance space that will captivate audiences around the globe.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2406, \"end\": 2411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.776260983737146e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Paralympics 2024 will feature22 sports, with 549 gold medals up for grabs.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.776260983737146e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether you are a fan of wheelchair basketball, or para-swimming, there is something for everyone, according to theLocal France.\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2709, \"end\": 2715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7297658465771051, \"rank\": 0.3702694483918308, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's Paralympics in Paris promises to be a celebration of athleticism, determination, and the spirit of competition.\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2745, \"end\": 2750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.776260983737146e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r